{
  "stem": "20021.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Most of the life in Russia was that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So anyhow, they looked around, moved around the house, and left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't bother to climb up on the haystack and look around for more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is 1940.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's about July, August.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that, there was one boy in our group whose parents were taken away and sent to Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He found himself alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he later went to the [INAUDIBLE], tell them, look, I managed to hide out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here I am.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm surrender.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wouldn't send him any more to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have transports anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- this was the type of Russian management that existed there, everything sort of loose and lax and unexplainable and-- Like in this case, on one hand you were a criminal.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were being sent to Russia because we were considered traitors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the other hand, you come, you surrender.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You say, the police was looking for me, here I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't bother him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wouldn't send--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, subsequently we were all given passports.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Russia, everybody has to have a passport, which is an identity card.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all given passports.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the passport was stamped with Paragraph 11, which means this person is sort of not to be trusted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's an enemy of the state.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as a result, we were not allowed to live in any large town, only small towns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not allowed to go to high school, which otherwise I would have been entitled to a free high school education.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Prior to that really, I did go for a short period of time to a Jewish high school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Russia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The language of instruction was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
